description: Pretty sus. Dont wear it around the wrong people.
name: Sus Costume
note:
<Variable 27 Buy Price: 120>
<Variable 27 Sell Price: 60>
<Custom On Equip Eval>
user._prevCharName = user._prevCharName || user._characterName;
user._prevCharIndex = user._prevCharIndex || user._characterIndex;
user._prevFaceName = user._prevFaceName || user._faceName;
user._prevFaceIndex = user._prevFaceIndex || user._faceIndex;
user._prevBattlerName = user._prevBattlerName || user._battlerName;

if (user.actorId() === 1){
user.setFaceImage("bambis_icons_extra", 0);
user.setCharacterImage("bambis_extra", 0);
user.setBattlerImage("BAMBISUS_1");
user.refresh();
}if (user.actorId() === 2){
user.setFaceImage("bambis_icons_extra_@", 4);
user.setCharacterImage("all sus", 1);
user.setBattlerImage("BAMBISUS_2");
user.refresh();
}if (user.actorId() === 11){
user.setFaceImage("bambis_icons_extra_@", 6);
user.setCharacterImage("all sus", 3);
user.setBattlerImage("BAMBISUS_3");
user.refresh();
}if (user.actorId() === 3){
user.setFaceImage("bambis_icons_extra_@", 5);
user.setCharacterImage("bambis2", 6);
user.setBattlerImage("BAMBISUS_4");
user.refresh();
}if (user.actorId() === 14){
user.setFaceImage("bambis_icons_extra_@", 7);
user.setCharacterImage("all sus", 2);
user.setBattlerImage("IKAMBISSUS1_1");
user.refresh();
}if (user.actorId() === 15){
user.setFaceImage("bambis_icons3", 4);
user.setCharacterImage("all sus", 4);
user.setBattlerImage("YAMBISSUS1_1");
user.refresh();
}

</Custom On Equip Eval>
<Custom On Remove Equip Eval>
user.setCharacterImage(user._prevCharName, user._prevCharIndex);
user.setFaceImage(user._prevFaceName, user._prevFaceIndex);
user.setBattlerImage(user._prevBattlerName );
user.refresh();
user._prevCharName = undefined;
user._prevCharIndex = undefined;
user._prevFaceName = undefined;
user._prevFaceIndex = undefined;
user._prevBattlerName = undefined;
$gamePlayer.refresh();
</Custom On Remove Equip Eval>
